[p 
	[em 
		"Star Trek: 25th Anniversary
	]em
	" is a point & click adventure game released in 1992 for DOS. It features the original 
	[em 
		"Star Trek
	]em
	" crew (Kirk, Spock, McCoy and 
	[a class=extlink href=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Redshirt_%28stock_character%29 rel=nofollow 
		"redshirt
	]a
	"). You play through seven episodes, each assigning you with a mission that you need to complete in order to go on with the next mission.
